title: Ethynyl-substituted benzosiloxaboroles: the role of C(π)⋯B interactions in their crystal packing and use in Cu(I)-catalyzed 1,3-dipolar cycloaddition
content:
RSC Adv., 2024, 14,16069-16082
DOI: 10.1039/D4RA02137A, Paper

P. Pacholak, K. Durka, K. Woźniak, J. Krajewska, A. E. Laudy, S. Luliński
Ethynyl-substituted benzosiloxaboroles feature distinctive C(π)⋯B interactions in the crystalline state and are useful in Cu(I)-catalyzed 1,3-dipolar cycloaddition reactions.
